        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A clearcoat is a separate layer of transparent specular highlights",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "used to simulate a clear coating, like on a car or the surface of",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "lacquered objects. Use this initializer to create an object to",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "specify the amount of clearcoat for a material using a single value",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "for the entire material, a UV-mapped image to specify different",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "values for different parts of the entity, or both.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The values from this property are available in the custom material’s",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "surface shader function regardless of the value of",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/CustomMaterial/lightingModel-swift.property",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " , but clearcoat",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "isn’t drawn unless the custom material’s",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/CustomMaterial/lightingModel-swift.property",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " is",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/CustomMaterial/LightingModel-swift.enum/clearcoat",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " and the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "surface shader calls ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "params.surface().set_clearcoat()",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The following Metal code demonstrates how to retrieve the scale and",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "texture values from this property and use them to enable clearcoat",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "rendering.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "    // Retrieve the clearcoat scale and roughness from the CustomMaterial.",
            "    float clearcoatScale = params.material_constants().clearcoat_scale();",
            "    float clearcoatRoughnessScale = params.material_constants().clearcoat_roughness_scale();",
            "",
            "    // Assign the clearcoat scale to enable clearcoat rendering (if",
            "    // lightingModel is .clearcoat).",
            "    params.surface().set_clearcoat(clearcoatScale);",
            "",
            "    // Assign the clearcoat roughness from the scale property set",
            "    //  on the custom material.",
            "    params.surface().set_clearcoat_roughness(clearcoatRoughnessScale);"
          ],
          "syntax": "other",
          "type": "codeListing"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
